;re investing in convenience, attractiveness, and effectiveness for your Shopify store.</p>\n\n\n	<p>Based on our 5 years of experience building Shopify themes, we have developed a product optimized to easily customize every part of your store through an intuitive dashboard. This allows you to set up quickly and easily without wasting time and effort.</p>\n\n\n	<p>With a team of experienced developers, we are always ready to support you and answer any questions you may have. We offer installation support for your online store. If you encounter any errors during the installation process, we will guide you through troubleshooting them. With professional and dedicated support, we aim to help you attract potential customers, increase conversion rates and create an excellent online shopping experience for your customers.</p>\n\n\n	<p>Scroll down or click on <a href=\"https://landing.thimpress.com/coma-shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Live Preview</strong></a> to explore the amazing features and surprises awaiting you.</p>\n\n\n	<p><a href=\"https://coma-demo.myshopify.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/new-update-103.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 4\" /></a></p>\n\n\n	<p><a href=\"https://coma-demo.myshopify.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/coma-new-demo.jpg\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 5\" /></a></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 6\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 7\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 8\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 9\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/6.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 10\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/7.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 11\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 12\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/9.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 13\" /></p>\n\n\n	<p><a href=\"https://help.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/10.png\" alt=\"COMA - Modern Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 14\" /></a></p>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"item-description__features\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n     <li>Easy to Import Demo Config (One-Click)</li>\n     <li>Social Share Feature</li>\n     <li>Multi-purpose Designs</li>\n     <li>Fast Loading, Optimized for mobile &#38; Better SEO</li>\n     <li>Responsive Design, Mobile Optimized &#38; Incredible UI/UX</li>\n     <li>Fully Responsive (Tested on Multiple Devices)</li>\n     <li>Modern &#38; Clean Design</li>\n     <li>Built with CSS 3 + HTML 5, Tailwind</li>\n     <li>Google Web Fonts Integration, Support Shopify,  Font Picker, Custom font</li>\n     <li>40+ Stunning Homepage Layouts</li>\n     <li>10+ Layouts Options for Category Page</li>\n     <li>19+ Layouts Options for Product Page</li>\n     <li>04+ Layouts Options for Tab Product</li>\n     <li>05+ Layouts for product description</li>\n     <li>06+ Blog page layouts</li>\n     <li>Multiple Headers, Footers</li>\n     <li>Custom header &#38; footer for special page</li>\n     <li>External &#38; Affiliate Product</li>\n     <li>Cart Modal/Cart Drawer/Cart Ajax/Cart Page</li>\n     <li>Order Note/Quickly Add A Coupon/Estimate Shipping</li>\n     <li>Numerous Custom Pages: Lookbook, FAQs, Contact Us, Portfolio, About us, Contact us, 404, Shop Instagram</li>\n     <li>Advanced Mega menu layouts</li>\n     <li>GRID &#38; LIST Mode</li>\n     <li>Product Reviews (App)</li>\n     <li>Zoom Magnifier Support</li>\n     <li>Ajax Product Filter Support</li>\n     <li>Support multi language and multi currency</li>\n     <li>Sticky Header</li>\n     <li>Quick Shop</li>\n     <li>Ajax Layered Navigation</li>\n     <li>Ajax Live Search</li>\n     <li>One Click Checkout</li>\n     <li>Advanced Size Chart (MaxSale app)</li>\n     <li>Custom Product Tabs</li>\n     <li>Login &#38; Registration page</li>\n     <li>GDPR Cookie Popup (App)</li>\n     <li>Sticky Add to Cart</li>\n     <li>Lookbook Module</li>\n     <li>Automatic Image resize</li>\n     <li>Ajax Infinite Scroll module + Ajax Load More + Pagination/ Product Count</li>\n     <li>Builder Sections on All page</li>\n     <li>Product Image Swap/ Advanced Product Swatches</li>\n</ul>\n<em>\n<strong>** Please note:</strong> Images used and included in this theme are for demo purpose only, NON-COMMERCE PURPOSE. They are not a part of the theme and are NOT included in the final purchase files.</em>\n<h4 id=\"item-description__changelogs\">CHANGELOGS</h4>\n<p><strong> Version 1.1.2 &#8211; 24-November-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>ADDED: NEW PAGE - Flash Sale\nFIXED: Some small errors.</pre>\n<p><strong> Version 1.1.1 &#8211; 19-November-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Removed discount code input feature from the cart page and sidebar cart.\nAdded Horizontal Filter functionality to the shop page.\nRemoved collection URLs from product links.\nFixed display issue when clicking the mobile menu.</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Version 1.1.0 &#8211; 02-August-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Added option to enable/disable Top Bar on Tablet and Mobile\nAdded Color configuration for Section Scrolling icons\nIntroduced new \"Ba