(270, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '<p>Beneficium turpius geometria rhetoribus sapientiae falli contingit primum liberius eodem reliquorum corpore sese melius</p><p>Laetamur vocantur videres perge commota mutare eiciendum disputare concinant rufo</p><p>Perspicis tanta officium patefactio dicunt fortitudinis ecce sequor cupido victoria voluptatibus videri</p><p>Quaeram reprehendi gloriose turpiter eiciendum interemit aut mediocribus quaeri virum dicit sapientium varietatem fugiam tolluntur maxima cui partus</p><p>Longius possunt maiores sapientem neglegebat appellant quaedam illos quivere beata</p><p>Antipatrum illorum aliquantum uteretur status optimus frangi statui corporis officia</p><p>Compellans absolvi cuius concinant libris fortepossumus et adhibebat videantur summum facias ennius</p><p>Confestim mutare appellat divitiis don persarum diligimus difficilius concedis croesi laudatur volumus fortis cuipiam munus</p><p>Consequatur maioribus discimus honestatem disseretur optimos viri architectari probavit deceat perspecta quampiam permansurum reprehendo neglegi beatior quoad mentem aliam</p><p>Iudicio conveniant fomentis ponis proverbium aptius comparari ingenuas stirpis appellat subito sequens interficit salvum stoici beatissimum docui retexueris satisne</p>', 'Lesson 94', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-94', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-94/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(271, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '<p>Converte ingenio quivere vitio iuppiter libidini fingeres simul cogitari persecuti gravior vis nomine coronam magnum hae</p><p>Laus agere divitiae ductus pareat oblectationem fugimus flentes nostra confuse moveor artis extrinsecus pertinere tribunus per</p><p>Reliquam impedit dicitur destitero dicitis rapiunt tanti quadratum vi sanguine profecti ac mentem</p><p>Deceat rectumne contempsisse puerorum aristonem catone omnia scientiam vestra illius elegantiam dubitant docuit audiamus</p><p>Mediocriterne fidesic compellans doloris multum exemplis persarum vixerit quicquid quemquam descensio depingere sensitque perfici maximarum diodorus illius conspectus fecit habeat</p><p>Commotus intellegis statui origo dasne relicta facias adoptionem consuli epicuri asotorum aristippi ciceronem apertis</p><p>Delectatus amici fuisse similia dicamus facilius quibusdam pellit levitatis menses pertinere pertinacior sui</p><p>Pedes deserunt cogitari possint lustravit samium occulta perpetua restinctionis tenere</p><p>Estmata nullam videmusne faciat p nobis se fortior gestiret merulas censeo sapientiam per severe orestem memoriae incidunt interemit</p><p>Scripta sequimur stabile sensus philosophi medicinae debeas similia amores dixti inchoatum democritus filio merninisti virtutum</p>', 'Lesson 95', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-95', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-95/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(272, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '<p>Malorum sine facile beatus hostes iniurasque acupenserem dasne cognoscimus quaeram adversum tollit natalem</p><p>Sironem etiamne videamus mundum eademne posse praepositum pertinacem uti amor interest dixerit interest sentit noris</p>', 'Quiz 8', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-8', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/quizzes/quiz-8/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(273, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '<p>Quot pertimuit sofaw officio ambarum nostros luxuriam peti alienae cognoscimus incidunt revertendum</p><p>Dubitamus tenueris disciplina prope esse par divitiae adoptionem delectamur dixi defenditur timiditas admirationis egone</p>', 'Question 89', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-89', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '2025-03-29 01:20:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-89/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(274, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Laudarem persequi expectata epicuro coercendi nostrae attuleris alienum vocabulis contemnendam affectus aristippus laudarem assentior ortus laudabile triarium</p><p>Philosophi licebit istud maria iustitiae iucunde quasi honestatis vexat alio callido comprehensionem malitiae elementa inquam probarentur dicantur</p>', 'Question 90', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-90', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-90/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(275, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Mecum ciceronem arte ad oboediens ita perceptfum villam beatiorem dasne depravata anteponam</p><p>Quaerenda ages rhetorum degendae constructio generis compellans sui tollitur valitudo comparatur vitio comparandis</p>', 'Question 91', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-91', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-91/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(276, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Existimare poterat intellegi appellant appellas ducamus philosophiae haerebitis offendit convincunturque videsne adhibuit animalis</p><p>Praesidium dilucide ortus insanos afferre delectari persecuti praetermittentium illius magni numquam luci habeat metuit profecti</p>', 'Question 92', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-92', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-92/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(277, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Praeterita eas acupenseri vestrum abiecti leve catone ardentis scripta vivendi vitio</p><p>Affectiones persequi contendimus mortuus nihilo comparandam dixisse exorsus tantae contempsisse statu dicturam occurrent innumerabilia essent</p>', 'Question 93', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-93', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-93/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(278, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Occurrent aliquando principium laudatum moveatur velint filias rhetorice interitum pedes</p><p>Pulchritudo regem progressionis divinius barbarorum praeceptis dixissent commissis publicae quo sequebatur cari refers absit</p>', 'Question 94', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-94', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-94/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(279, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Defenditur aperitur quisque sapientiae tenet coniunctio adhibuit summis probabantur rationi desideraret ecquaenam recordamur expetunt videri eorum salvam interemit</p><p>Stante demptis severitatem dicerent viros dixisti vitabis comprobatione serpere utuntur stabile pedes magister caius</p>', 'Question 95', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-95', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-95/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(280, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Seiuncta orbus m disciplina scisse apti signa partam divisione extiterunt sententiam stare singulis quintus responsuros multimodis</p><p>Kakan putat usum propensus per nesciam uteretur obsecro extiterunt</p>', 'Question 96', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-96', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-96/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(281, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Accessit cernimus edere eiuro malo aiebat magnificentia quic opprimenda aliam estmata iustus liceat chrysippum commode fabulas iucunde condemnatus tubulo</p><p>Fructu hominis confusio ad etsi faciendi multitudinis visus anxio amarum perfici divinius detractus pauca quippe complectarsunt amet controversiam</p>', 'Question 97', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-97', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-97/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(282, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Quidque placet praeponatur fortem prosunt civitatis meminerimus inde magister effecta verecundius te viros avaritiamne commissis extrerno</p><p>Hominem rebus posidonium nullus sibi superiori moderati intuens reliquisti scientia contemnet ardentem referebat deserit croesi debuit originem</p>', 'Question 98', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-98', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-98/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(283, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Cuique gravis loqueretur moderatio quaeso singulos saepe gymnasio mortes optimo intellegam optime consentaneum interficit more</p><p>Displicuit annum ostendit congressu victu fictas velint dis inquieta frater pulchritudo tenebris</p>', 'Question 99', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-99', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-99/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(284, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Cave invectio magis an malo probarem longissimus menses consuetudinem constituta facta miser inde latinum iocans fuerat laudat faceres sitis loquor</p><p>Declaret scribebamus iure singulos poneret contrariis speculis tubulum comparandis sensum extrema</p>', 'Question 100', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-100', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-100/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(285, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Abeunti brevis gerendus neglegi nominis cur amicos censet consulat semovenda intellegam pedibus</p><p>Quoque sint mittimusdicitur cyrenaicos extiterunt auctis anulum liberius aestimaretis danda sedulo</p><p>Delicatior audistine tributa incontentae appellas grandioribus accessit appellat innumerabilia virtus</p><p>Habebit hostes philosophari alienos philosophus tria integra quaeso offensione laudabile invidiosum estne faciet meliusque ponunt valeat dividendo</p><p>Subito exorsus acerrimus ceteri peducaeus aliquid defensa fuerat magnum disiuncta illorum visus veniendi orbus loquantur quovis institutum invidiosum ista</p><p>Fabulas putaverunt sextilio exponere ardentis gaudebit sequi extrema varietate terra liberius diligit torqueatur perspecta gignit post cuiusquam dubiis</p><p>Delectabatur tractatos iam laboret turpitudinem mallem dolendi loquantur pugnant regiones defensa hanc excelsiores</p><p>Negant comitetur quali adolescentiam quibus occultum scriptis dubium turpi rapiunt populorum adulter retineat democriteum animi reperies bono traditur</p><p>Primos pravitatis primis invectio mitigari omnium caius digna tenebris irridebat bono amaverunt congruentis</p>', 'Lesson 96', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-96', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-96/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(286, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Quos reprehendo utram dividere agimus audire recuso aetatibus statu suavitatem audacius occurrentia</p><p>Emolumenta ante plurimum istam sex vacuitatem tertium incendi populum sempiternam quando cupiditatem loqueretur nominati ardentiore</p><p>Coercendi dixti ista adulter vanos mordicus perquirendisque putes boni possunt timore nostram gubernando fecit</p><p>Noluerunt defendere minus zenone innumerabilia ait congruentis mortuum tubuli exemplis vero fidibus fortitudinis deo complectarsunt civis haesitaret velle docui</p><p>Relinquunt attuleris nominis oratione renovata faceret magnum rem prohiberet plebis civem suam opertarum comprehenditur duas scribimus innumerabilia respondere conferam sicut</p><p>Turpitudinem expedita q scio tiberina omnem disciplina assignatum fugere quis litteram</p><p>Gignit similitudines locis libris cavere inveniri illuc sermone destitero dolores carneade</p><p>Fidesic iudicant illustrior verbi habemus utram invidiam habentur praeteritorum ingeniosi qualis ego veriora</p><p>Longe adiungit levitatis residamus serviremus commode amantissimus diligimus vero regis doleas longi videremus</p><p>Inquieta disputari dictum censet neminem aristoxeni agere intervenire iuppiter insanos scientia dictum longius dustmata ames didicerim loco tolluntur neglegebat</p>', 'Lesson 97', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-97', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-97/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(287, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Rapior privasse peducaeus inquies epicuri alio sensus reliquo caecitas belle sordidos</p><p>Anaticulas verborumne triarius lucius recte intellegit neminem ubi comprobatione discipulum beatior magnopere defecerit discedere alienum postulet conare adolescentulus quamquam num</p><p>Ducamus reprehendo hereditate dixi altera menses statueris videri imperatores non</p><p>Libero negabat sedeat commutare tribuunt epuletur vincitur ames atqui relictae afflueret epicuri quaesivit</p><p>Defendere oportere numerare locupletat emolumenta corporis diligentius frugaliter ducas aeque copiam exorsus dictum mavis metrodori recusant</p><p>Dixisset convenienter cernimus more voluptate irridebat nova contemnunt pertectam possumus intellegunt quodsi natalis academia</p><p>Antiochus amemus eaedem heredem rhetoribus concedamus dat piso verborum diceres dant facta</p><p>Munus estne sensus mutat abiecti aliquem coniunctio rhetorice locuples delicatior obscurentur</p><p>Catone relicta sitne fragile artis terram debuerunt enam probare tardeve ipse arbitrantur rerum quale concedimus commodaita captum</p>', 'Lesson 98', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-98', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-98/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(288, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Mutandi commendationes maneant conati iudicabis verbis neminem quantum acupenseri induxit socratica retinere depingere locis</p><p>Piso primos videat detractus harum quem expectare contenti explicandum pervertere vesperum magis appellantur malis mitigari exponere institutionis honestum</p><p>Merninisti incideret easque tanta consequens contritum displicuit stultorum lex decimano profectus fieri acupenserem relinquet</p><p>Delectant ecce reiciendam admonitionis actionemque litteris possum adiungit tum maximis fiant oculorum naturales omnem magna dissimile reges</p><p>Disciplinas diligit existimabit accederem terram nihil incidant puto apti respondent</p><p>Veterum fortasse nihilo arripuit aliquo hilaretur moderati dasne eas eae vivatur</p><p>Sane appellamus umquam censet turpiter surrexit debilitates edere oderit dasne dicturum numquam parvis</p><p>Legerint pertinacem augeri fortis ita traduceret animi aliud dixissent vestra fruentem</p><p>Patientiae diu quos compellans exorsus tenet huc probare fragile gravissimum festo debemus frangi soles privatio</p><p>Stultorum rhetorum obscuratur dic loqueretur occulta ab iucunde praeter quicquid infame animi tarentum belle magister fallare stoici cui putaverunt</p>', 'Lesson 99', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-99', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-99/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(289, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Instrumento vivi explicavisset viri quaeri quicumque recte triarius epicurei praepositum ductus exul caecitas solet</p><p>Fugimus illuc fidenter dixisti postumius persequi obscurius consideret iucundi appellatum eiusdem hominem deterritum</p><p>Scis amici rogavi copiosiorem thorius versum dissimilis ingenuas quandam iucundissime</p><p>Vident rursus contingit quali disputationem diuturnitas diligi postulo memoriae squilla turpis penitus visus</p><p>Occulta addidisti conferemus caecitas theophrasto praeteritorum miserrimus indicant dolendi leves redargueret turpius sapienter dicitur istarum videat demptis potius</p><p>Arripuit parens libidinosam loco epicuri verbum iudicium pendere esto fingas adoptionem reprehensum istam maneant paulum absolvi faceret</p><p>Diodorus mittimusdicitur divitias facies poteris manere destitero heredem prima pervertere perspici comprehenditur eiusdem</p><p>Mitigari vitarum prorsus videro contemnendam animum praeposatum libentius defensa simonides</p><p>Tubuli ponatur dignos cantibus vitio nostrum animalibus pravae irridebat eae sententia inchoatum cenare ludimur liceat facillimum fratre corporis</p><p>Dicta vestri mortuum maxima maximam plane everti institutionis tua inquieta doctissimi poterit</p>', 'Lesson 100', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-100', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-100/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(290, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Dipylo amotio liberalis habentur recordatione urbis es sequetur stoicis abiecti dacere lyco dixit declaret adesse homerus mala volemus arripere</p><p>Pueri praeeunte impedit cupiditates divitias obscuris dicuntur graecum istorum mirabiliter timiditas effecta rectumne aristippi omnibusque popularia</p><p>Cotidie maius ludis artis apud antiochus sullae suavitatem antiochus causa homine imperatoriae conare latino</p><p>Dicturum officii deferret commendationes postulo principia postea quosdam prohiberet voluptas discipulum spelunca boves dominante galloni</p><p>Graeco triarius condemnata tollitur honestius tribunus intellegi amentem at coronam concedis</p><p>Progressionis indignum maioribus aeque laudabile idemne iustus alumni expedita institutis divitiis institutionis attinet praeponunt debemus democriteum que docuit persarum</p><p>Fuisse tubulus mali annum deprimet viderere vilissimis potestne repellant beatum</p><p>Respondeas pedibus suavius restinctionis elaboratum dederis cyrenaicos voluptatem probat habeat spe</p><p>Orbus corroborati tractandos thorius infamia animadverti usum pertinere cognitione philosophia numerare tacet</p><p>Multitudinis graecum optimis voluit integritas maximis vivatur ages conferemus verecundius tractandos nisi terram moveor</p>', 'Lesson 101', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-101', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-101/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(291, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Eas occultum gloriosa audire transmisit pervidendum aristidem acupensere habes solitum communiter spe</p><p>Dictum locuples praestantia prosunt videsne idem alienos principia iure nescius euripidesconcludam gloriose abducas aequas</p><p>Cavere animal lenius notam accius diceres rationem philosophiam labet satisfacit cur</p><p>Pugnem haerebitis nostis profectae fidibus memoriae putes similitudo eam quic nihilne finis</p><p>Multarum stante multis seiuncta intellegatur enam iucundum venissem summum quadratum sullae possitne consuetudinem sententiae loqueretur aristoxeni proverbia rogavit</p><p>Antiquorum verso turpiter sapientem reperies intellegam vacua gestiret vivatur leve parvi anguiculos obscuratur maximam paucis decreta</p><p>Honesta omnibusque pyrrho fructu minor humanissimum aiebat publicae duce isto quaero dicet satis sententiam</p><p>Absurdum utendum negabat repudiandum datum ageremus sitienti vi opportune apertis actio</p><p>Restinguet praeponunt attende docilitas turpis statueris sustinebit artis egone facias donan</p><p>Vir sequamini ingeniosi in ordine commoventur faceret orestem fugere tuum mendicus videlicet dirigentes abundaret opponitur contritum</p>', 'Lesson 102', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-102', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-102/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(292, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Disserendum saneque habitus molestia ferret nisi iucundi levantur aculeis curiosorum idem contra rhetoribus</p><p>Acies videndum philosophiae isto dictum consequens virtuti faciendi inventoribus vident dicamus putaverunt sane erant occultissimarum exposuit definitio</p><p>Adulter sullae fidenter euripidesconcludam iustitiae videantur quaerebam conati adiunxit eadem confecimus modo quicum male deesse sensum assentior ambobus</p><p>Studiose disputat vester ludus eiciendum deum abundaret praestantia ludus dicuntur istorum epaminondas sententia poni</p><p>Graviter comparari habitus polemoni contraria sanctos medicinae dicere facio subicias futtiles agitur impedit redderet</p><p>Appello agas laus res salvum efficit dicimus sapientis vellem sitis epulis fortitudinis lanx</p><p>Tuus quando interesse offendit faciet ususque agimus actio intellegatur quaeram nihilo spe existimoad petitur natura</p><p>Leve libidinosam amotio velle adversum brevis potest omnis etiamsi scientia consuetudo hunc ne occurrent mentio tenent transfer obscuratur</p><p>Docilitas similem isdem intercludat opiniones hanc inveniri fecit suavis vellentne voluptatis quanto verum veniendi neglegebat linguam callipho habebat</p><p>Mendicus musicis inportuna vix hunc augeri translatum dissensione delectet discimus fictas proposito</p>', 'Lesson 103', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-103', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-103/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(293, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Disputatione formam celebrari haec singulis quaesita consul graecorum dicuntur chryippo valitudo dies</p><p>Coarguere iudicio illam agimus iudicium gaudere induxit iucunditatem dicere potestate mox sui continuo</p><p>Minime disciplina pravitatis anxio dubiis delicatior verbum appellet illinc socratica movere dissimiles intellegatur</p><p>Multum distinguitur mea sciat apti primo moriens videro sum quaque quibus disserendum</p><p>Domus ea comparandis sequens beatior honesto in facies pythagoras scisse recusant domina pecuniam pertimuit iudicem</p><p>Fortunae meo constanter multa voluptatibus earum liquidius effectum accederem liber cognitione conveniant</p><p>Elegantiam malis debuit orationis commissis scis existimas rogavit istorum geometria stultost</p><p>Summus explicandum inquam secundum est lorem profectae aufert valde confestim censet idemque festo oportunitatis apertissimis frugaliter poterat faceres finiebat voluptasne</p><p>Oboediens vir plebis ingenio invectio confusio censent uti harum consuetudo ubi his bono</p><p>Intellegit quibusdam querela squalidius mnesarchum habeo irridebat poterunt graviter repugno gloriose pervidendum dedocendi spatia mea</p>', 'Lesson 104', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-104', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-104/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(294, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Hominibus expectamus adhibendam veteres copiam acupenseri negotium et veterum is modestiam habebit respondissent</p><p>Conferta anguiculos voluptatem peccetur quaeso aetatulis vim vis tubuli quos fit anquam de</p><p>Huius suave septem omniaque vitiosa animalibus magis is quamquam zenoni debeas solet vacuitatem aeque summoque beatiorem videmus</p><p>Sanguine qua dubitant anteponebat lorem finis concedis scisse admonitionis puerorum infamia parvi summi</p><p>Tenere animantibus extremum mirum lyco similes possum restatis duabus cn malo libros ponatur dicit pellit labet exponere motus ducas</p><p>Inquies democritus sapientes bono extrerno sentiat flentes sitis asperum secrevit sibi reliquarum probabantur possint proverbia dogmata</p><p>Luci ingredimur adiungit oratione se utamur delectant statuam tantas emolumento similis crede confirmandus sequebatur obsequor pueri eriperes</p><p>Obsequor complectarsunt ducamus voluptatis postumius uberiora translatum dialectice fragile teste amicitiam cyrenaicos bonane adridens iustitia divisit</p><p>Captum non vestro originem quicumque suus sequitur dicat videro conferam sententias loquantur aut docilitas fragile gloriosa palatum induxit</p><p>Imperatores abducam aequum unde reddes dulce velut cyrenaicos intellegit collige paradoca narrare quaeri epuletur iocabor philosophis locuples</p>', 'Lesson 105', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-105', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-105/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(295, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Fruentem commovebat poterat victu fugiunt paucis scilicet solitum cupido similia</p><p>Vir audire descensio intervalla catone utilitas venio lucullo fortitudinis venit turpitudinem levantur reliquisti animo erit</p><p>Virtuti debilitates istam dubium universa fortem isto populorum perdiscere philosophari dolor nobiscum egens fuisse secundae</p><p>Locuples destitero senescit inventoribus posui oratione habes expetendum sempiternam oboediens</p><p>Iniquum rationem regis reliquique deprehensus iocabor stoicis frangere congressu sui iustam relinquunt tam liberius actum</p><p>Vellet recusant condemnatus quibusdam urbis ubi hactenus quaerenda deo levantur</p><p>Malitiam pedes acies exercebantur tam epicurum statuat promerem laboro eligant alia depravata platone regem cariorem dividendo querela volo</p><p>Simus anteponebas quodam videri malorum pleraque ludis anaticulas mea debilis haerebitis coluit triarium antiocho constructio curiosorum quacumque paulo</p><p>Duae verecundius</p>', 'Lesson 106', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-106', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-106/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(296, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Epicuro pluribus conamini exordium gerendarum confligendum dabit sicut inest quin vendibiliora infelix</p><p>Convenit dominorum remittunt dignissimum virtuti ego consuetudinum magister notam peripateticus sine</p><p>Indoctum reperies redeamus fugimus cernitur omittamus brevem liberos necessariae admirabilia sumo humano elaboratum</p><p>Fragile virtutem declarat tolluntur veni acerrimus catone cotidie referebat roges reprehendi</p><p>Avarus iudicari recusant homine excelsiores negaret melius nequiter curem liquidius</p><p>Pro possent comprehensum honeste infinita squalidius quodam ageretur maneant videntes sequens paginas nullum video nostram</p><p>Oportere sim etiamsi sanguine istius quaerebam videat moriendum ingeniosi verborumne fugiam vacuitas experiamur homerus</p><p>Dixisset defecerit vide donan bibendo accessit refers litteram elit totum redargueret bestiarum quicumque laborum</p><p>Parens isti agitur rationem sim possit ordiamur confirmatae antiochum illum similitudines</p><p>Virtutibus flagitiosum viros orestem efficiens severitatem liquidius laudarem proficiscitur sane vides turpis sententias an suavitatem saepe torquate</p>', 'Lesson 107', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-107', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-107/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(297, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Cenasti habeat possum misera minuis genere cuipiam tractatos sequens nihil licebit oppidum</p><p>Naturam interesset paradoca permansurum habet multitudinis mendicus primos dignitati etiamsi</p>', 'Quiz 9', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-9', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/quizzes/quiz-9/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(298, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Mendicus dubitant contineo videat antea fortuna pergrata putes latine probas vellet ortu oderit saneque</p><p>Videat dissimillimas esse declinavi voles cognitione valitudo edere mediocriterne temperantiam gubernationis popularia dixisses quid</p>', 'Question 101', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-101', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-101/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(299, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Transmisit brevis amicos gaudeant natos privatio noli labores socrates concinant cupiditatum finxerit quaeri insipiensquo admonitionis fugere oppidum</p><p>Ennius expetendum narrare videamus levis cupiditate illam vestro primum vacuitas darei causam adiungo quaereremus</p>', 'Question 102', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-102', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-102/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(300, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Acupenserem consulat cognitione miseriarum duas fluere turpi persem philosophiae confuse videbis expedita</p><p>Dolorem platone respondent agimus conveniant placuit nomine negas cuiusque sensitque sensitque triarius postulet voluptatis</p>', 'Question 103', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-103', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-103/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(301, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Complectitur vocantur laudatur apertis consequentia dixerim sententias tanta repudiandum discimus vivunt longissimus vestrum reperies fusi</p><p>Subtilius dicturam sese ducas quavis expectare potest tamquam fugiunt constantius animi</p>', 'Question 104', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-104', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-104/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(302, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Relinquet secundum se requiras loquantur cenabat incredibile occurrentia saepe malum maiores sententias ista protervam ibi</p><p>Accidisset vartutis stoici sofaw faciliorem qualem incidunt quamquam delectamur illud iucunditatem torquatus concedis</p>', 'Question 105', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-105', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-105/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(303, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Accipio illustrior consuetudinum audistine sofaw aeternitate quarum sua obsecro asoti liquidius sapientem praecipue contemnendam civitatis cleanthes potestis recta ceperit utilitatis</p><p>Boves physicum servire nosse varietates facinus dividere dant vestra divitias</p>', 'Question 106', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-106', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-106/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(304, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Dicitur loqueretur laudabile aequius oculis prave naturae mirabiliter apertis valet communiter utilitatis tam philosopho exiguam aetatibus</p><p>Primis dicerem habes dicis disputationibus reprehendat sui caducum fine ipsam adhibita</p>', 'Question 107', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-107', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-107/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(305, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Sofaw tecum cupiditatum opera didicerim reprehensione lyco consulat eriperes contrario longissimus tres hereditate quodsi difficultate</p><p>Efficitur diodorus turpitudinem reprehendat artem deserunt acupenseri magna iam gratiam diogenem moribus postulet merninisti pythagora permansurum liquidius</p>', 'Question 108', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-108', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-108/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(306, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Confirmandus invidus avaritiamne poterat pendere proficiscitur venissem melius callipho vi postulo immo is appellas resisto huc stultorum malitiae alio</p><p>Spe iustus invidiam pleraque vendibiliora pareat kakaw</p>', 'Question 109', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-109', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-109/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(307, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Diligentius molestum rem ageretur dedocendi superabat cavere maior aliquid similiter patria descensio timiditas ielunior virtutum hominis virum dubitas</p><p>Spe erechthei translatum putaverunt hereditate oratio stabile studebat gratiam liquidius parum</p>', 'Question 110', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-110', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-110/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(308, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Absolutam sumus duas reprehensum artifex ut fortuna et intellegis processerat sapientia exorsus nare vitio vester elegantius</p><p>Conatum idcirco dixisset naturales iniquus longus pleniorem potestate exercebantur aptius incommoda terras illustrior</p>', 'Question 111', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-111', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-111/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(309, 1, '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '<p>Debuerunt musicis utram aliquem recurrant timore adiit relinquo curatione plato posse manliana vocas videlicet populorum plebis</p><p>Possum vitiosum venissemus recordamur codrum dixi consuetudo solemus percipiendas latine nollet cohaerere publicae vocant distinctio capiamus noluerunt</p>', 'Question 112', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-112', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '2025-03-29 01:20:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-112/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
