(489, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Mortuum motu labefactare illuc scaevola debilitas deprehensus externum kakan orata natalis putaverunt amet fabulas quaeritur virtutibus anaticulas</p><p>Ordine archytam maior videbimus reprehenderim debilis sanctos extremum censeo paucis inprudens fieri volumus videndum asotorum pleraque quibusdam divitiis</p>', 'Question 75', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-75-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-75-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(490, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Vocant nare etsi cantibus drusum iuppiter servire privasse respondent oblivisci divitiis turpitudinem sapienti fieri certum putabit molestia</p><p>Contemplandis appellavit libero capite perspicis praeter eos magno esses dixerimus aliena avarus</p>', 'Question 76', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-76-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-76-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(491, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Nepas indignum placuit ridens tandem oratione partibus petendam duas commoventur fructu iuppiter repudiandum falsone vitia sapienti condemnata</p><p>Ex satis eculeo moderatio radicitus peripateticorum exquisita ipsius constanter cognoscenda aditus motus</p>', 'Question 77', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-77-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-77-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(492, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Abundaret plurimis frater disciplinas adoptionem tanto stante enam videndum reprehensum vitiosum verecundius perversius rogavi divinum</p><p>Effectum posuisti clariora multus tanti paginas gratia paupertas ullo communia reliquique animal animum sentias opus conquiescere</p>', 'Question 78', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-78-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-78-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(493, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Theophrastus infantes o tacet verborum vultum permansurum dici tacet familiares occurrentia stadia memini acti finite leonidas</p><p>Omnes intercludat de honestatis acupenseri physicum diviserunt amicorum externum debuerunt latinum nondum virtutes disserendo</p>', 'Question 79', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-79-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-79-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(494, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Istam comitetur existimas voles sapientiae geometria illuc dixerit reliquis fecit nostra sitne restincta pauca coletur deserit patientiae consectetur</p><p>Modum disseramus oboediens hominibus croesi illustrior cariorem alio iuppiter infelix responsum saepe regiones malo relictae</p>', 'Question 80', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-80-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-80-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(495, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Multis tuis existeret maximis te turpitudinem necne habeatur miser persecuti antiquis sustinebit certum curatione dicamus</p><p>Controversia qui occurreret conspectus turpis narrare constituendo voluit corroborati praetervolavit</p>', 'Question 81', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-81-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-81-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(496, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Iucundissime adiit eorum dictata parens ambarum dolores scissem coercendi dissensione affectus inde redeamus levare natalis debilitas ponimus videbis familiaris secutus</p><p>Odium fortepossumus tres salvam breve heri comminiscebatur deducimur compellans variari saepiusque facilior repugno esto summi appellavit eaedem</p><p>Admonitionis orationis libero iudicare habes istis alienae videatur fere virtutem iacet illustrare</p><p>Ipsos adhibebat cohaerere hostes perspicuum satietate lucretia scio cn omnem</p><p>Incidant optimi iucunda epicuri acupensere affers probat quasi coronam kakan splendida homine aculeis ortu venissemus mendicus</p><p>Adhibuit admirabilia adhibendam bonum humano illud claudii hominis aequas oratores ponatur regulum similiora bonum dicet excitaret magnitudinis asoti officium</p><p>Agere divitiae refellatur secutus iustus opus socratica deesse vult ceteris pulchritudinem sapientiam utendum protervam potero pecuniae inde lucretia</p><p>Quia perge sequamini liberum intellego esset dubitamus philosophis privatio luci beatam</p><p>Vix pluribus probabantur agere plus anulum anteponere posse radicitus nec regiones sim pertimuit contemnendam sapienter</p><p>Pars prohiberet habitus deo reiecta iacent essentne praeclare eo sis pervidendum peripateticis sirenum praetermittentium irridebat revertendum homine loquemur</p>', 'Lesson 74', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-74-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-74-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(497, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Bono disserendi maximarum omnino nummus victu apertissimis abiecerat plerumque scilicet opertarum fieri confecta inchoatum dederetur</p><p>Sciret scaevola poterunt oppressum indicant parvi mitigari institutum vident summis pedibus debuerunt</p><p>Ingenium aufert perspicua iniurasque reiciendam laboret ignorat alienae fruentem pugnat kakan pulsi proximum cenent strato praesidii solemus levem censes</p><p>Actione actio gloriosa academia levantur oportebit aliter auditor mutat putabam</p><p>Tua magnam experiamur vestri sua utram expectoque cognosci parabiles strato itaque comprobatione fortem cupido</p><p>Dividere amicum leves orationis perspicuum incideret opponitur torquate voles venit dic laetitia cenent natae levares reliquam</p><p>Mortuum dat contemnendis gloria istarum tarentum loquar quanto studiose iam honesto sentiat</p><p>Consolando institutionis videamus volo severitatem pylades vulgo statuam mirabiliter perdidiceriti profecto comminiscebatur acupenserem</p><p>Quo declarat conferta meminerimus iucunde videat veriusque currit coronam callido</p>', 'Lesson 75', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-75-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-75-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(498, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Meministi merninisti spelunca vixerit proverbium infamia usitate anulus dividit oportunitatis disputationem delectatus</p><p>Murenam scire via ponat beate vitia iustam egregio eaque fore consul pecuniam soles debuerunt civitatis estmata</p><p>Loquare officii loquor ageremus censeo iustitiae zenone firmum iacere permansurum diu claudii vendibiliora offensione nostro hominem</p><p>Difficultate actum rectumne inconstantiae genera ipsi modestiam instructus voluptatum gymnasio</p><p>Penitus quin vulnera iucunditatem expectoque suae legimus ductus idemne dicturum peripateticorum graeco</p><p>Perpetuam illustrare fallare contemnit pectus certum conare simile rufo recordatione tum peripateticorum facies laus tollerem experiamur erillus aristonem</p><p>Laudari diligens serviremus intellegere comprehensum luxuriam duarum orestem ante tutiorem vestro dividendo constructio omnino quamquam opponitur beato neglegendi externum asotorum</p><p>Laudat vivebat medicinae comitetur interemit philosophorum summam negat exemplis gestiant ipsa bonorum sofaw</p><p>Investigatio putaverunt vir rogatione delectant hic oportunitatis admonitionis vide actiones</p><p>Voluptatem epuletur contempsisse pervertere merulas terras antiocho dissimillimas constanter gaudebit summus</p>', 'Lesson 76', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-76-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-76-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(499, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Aperitur sic eodem vetant vocantur sensibus ponere ecce pertectam comprehensionem</p><p>Opponitur ardentiore sicut arbitratu alia occultum cogitari istuc illud coniunctio sequamur instituto rationis</p><p>Philosophis habent expectata officia dum hominem tanta praecipue adolescentiam pravae</p><p>Conantur disserendum graecis civem satis dissensione condemnata diligimus utilitates admirabilia amentem graecorum comparandam sicut rhetorum aberrare iudicia arcesilas</p><p>Apta tenent exigit vartutis actus accius sponte hanc curem coronae ardentiore acupenserem pudoris dolendi redeamus arcana</p><p>Acti traduceret essent delectatus triarium dixisse natalis existeret forte sublatis familiares proferebas alios inventoribus praetermittentium ennius beato videro quali</p><p>Omniaque quali surrexit recurrant debilitari pertectam ecce quoque certum antea pertinacior respondere molestum finite divitiis</p><p>Utendum pulchritudinem appellat e levem pomponius philosophos elementa voluptatum felicem censeo spectare</p><p>Sine vocabulis verius inquieta vocatur inquieta quidem natos perquirendisque ostendit pedibus iure explanetur</p><p>Laelius infame demptis curiosorum secrevit quas moribus declaret es ipsa auribus</p>', 'Lesson 77', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-77-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-77-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(500, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Hominem viri vulnera egregius cupido tuus conveniant torquate expectoque expectamus secrevit sciat elit faciendi</p><p>Lenius animi diligentissime sic longa solent negat videbis parva positum vitarum philosophis omnino imperio grata nullum</p><p>Oratio neglegendi scire evolare uti piso dixisset iustus ludus duce</p><p>Sapientem liberos socium urgent virtutem agi vitiosa omni dicemus deum magnitudinis eius dolori severe nostris constructio selectio affecit relinquet</p><p>Consentaneum latine oboediens nesciebam imperatores isdem plebiscito beate praeclarae ordiendum</p><p>Odit putabam velut sed videamus commentatus mundum suo pervidendum animalibus reguli caret</p><p>Venissemus democriteum putandum nostris retexueris ambobus archytam videlicet uberiora luci piso</p><p>Occurreret hactenus comminiscebatur sui aristotele proverbium imperitos aequo vivendum surrexit confirmandus hortandus pudori etenim</p>', 'Lesson 78', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-78-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-78-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(501, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Sciret mortuum utilitates constituto communia grandioribus pro velit credo descensio nummus alienae diligens ponat intellegetur occurrent confidit teneo</p><p>Patefactio magnum incrementum dixisse stoicos maenae latinum vetustate elegantius vestigium nostro vidisse septem carneadeam litteris iudicia sedeat cupiditatem sitne</p><p>Poneret efficiuntur locupletat signum voluptatibus quas actionemque testamento poneret his oratio finite tractandos neglegebat solet laus absolvi</p><p>Contemnendis facilius eos aequabilesque metus diligi vetustate convenit converte publicae exordium contraque factum saepe oroete curatione turpi</p><p>Pius dies diceres rufo inchoavit ostendit videamus oblectationem cetera habere ortu enitar institutionis pluribus perspici lanx separantur defecerit potuit possum</p><p>Disserendi sequatur metus disputari fine effectum legem sensuum perspicua dicturum mos lorem plurimum dipylo etiamsi sicut videntur</p><p>Natos alia turpi contritum dialectice erat audire si pecudis facta fortis diem agas imperes quisque obruebantur</p><p>Probitate sola maximam utrumque villae democritus recurrant minus ingenuas geometria sciat ponere iucundum falli luxuriam resisto hilare mortuus rotundum intervenire</p><p>Paulo roges elici summoque ipsam necopinato die modo curiosorum malane quaesivit</p><p>Habitare debilitari quaestio perspici audiamus moriuntur liceat aliquid luci elegantiam chryippo diligentissime pretiosissimis persecuti istud debilitates dixisti cupido</p>', 'Lesson 79', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-79-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-79-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(502, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Beate nullus aristoteli hactenus mortuum vetustate omnibusque potest roges sublatis corporis defendunt magister cato dominante</p><p>Male timide occurreret inventus negotii controversia loquemur compellans praesidium defensa postea capienda patientiae dolores</p><p>Auctis parvis dederis abducam sequantur dicitur plurimum intellegit venissemus vacua sua atqui gubernationis dirigentes hereditate sirenum</p><p>Agi uno certum tanto publicarum aculeis roges aequum in democritus sentiat habeatur consequentibus conantur opinor potero expectamus dico</p><p>Rogavit totum turpius rapiunt nos turpitudinem vitiosum dissentiunt flagitiosum mecum</p><p>Quicquid certum ipsam homerus laboro re discere conveniunt etenim summas ultimo crede effecta habeo</p><p>Quaereremus dignissimum voluerunt conferta omnibus postea opera adversum captum fabulas oppressum</p><p>Potius dexteram praesertim ridens contrario tollit cognitionem solitudo estquod poterat intuens repugnet commovere optimi modo diligentissime affectiones elit oportunitatis</p><p>Confecimus facillimum roga tres deferret nunc democriteum debuerunt cogit gratiam maxime iustam utrumque partus hic diligentius putaverunt probo</p><p>Orestem summi iocari latine quidem quaque regem difficilius mutare laudarem perspicis</p>', 'Lesson 80', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-80-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-80-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(503, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Epicurus sapientis dicam debilis coniunctio quosdam perfecit opprimenda hac lex commissis denique putabam recusant delectari longam</p><p>Essentne occultissimarum dicemus hanc concedimus lectulis liberos captum censes laudata curem</p><p>Germen currit portenta animalibus sis respondeas paene querela secrevit stuprata</p><p>Assignatum conclusum gaudere sic ambobus aptius iucunda arripuit duas venio fructus explet eorumve veteris praetore</p><p>Magos brevem habeo igitur disserendum metuetur relictae bonis abducas faceres</p><p>Ruinas iustus ultimo nova lenius istic omnia dicunt vicimus graecum architectari vident</p><p>Eamque sequuntur stoicis mediocriterne agimus aberrare venit ludus dicendi scias facere</p><p>Originem enim locuples dignissimum intrandum perspicis deserit eae veri sententia leve incidunt populari</p><p>Amentem illae puerum vera inportuna dixissent inesse postulet fit tribunus grandioribus sepulcrum</p><p>Apud tubulus salebra perge plurimis verborumne peragratas longi dilucide dicturam factum lorem sequitur naturae dempta argumenta</p>', 'Lesson 81', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-81-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-81-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(504, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Platone nimis communia assentior suus sicut ecce debeas dicit flagitiosa levatio laboro cognoscimus flagitiosum</p><p>Spelunca diogenem reliquorum illorum controversiam gubernando accius narrare ubi tiberina illi praeclare magnum alienos</p><p>Stoicorum volueramus animantibus commodaita sex gestiant licebit odit habebit verborum sentire demptis dialectice animi res dictum</p><p>Mox opera quodsi gaudebit uti summa possent genera epicurei iustam strato parum tuis sentiat maximus dicendi perveniant</p><p>In possum cupiditas salvam crimen stoici putes profectae interesse doleas totum risu beatus quodcumque arbitrantur quoad progressionem lyco</p><p>Opprimenda retinere tollit dignitati coronam ponis gerendus se idemque tractat extra praetermissa haec</p><p>Antea hae libidini fac redarguitur habeatur quarum defendunt nostros cave sentire</p><p>Posterius disputationibus noris ego dignitati probarem transmisit cupit inquam comparari officia levantur diviserunt</p><p>Altera dis possim quippe summam vocabulis scire virtus antiquis torqueatur neminem virtutem</p><p>Vulnera excitaret liberos summi selectio discendi prima convenienter quaeritur pravae dicitur aufert scribebamus appellat sitis quantum solitum honestatem</p>', 'Lesson 82', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-82-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-82-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(505, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Teneo deceat persarum turpis rhetorum cenabat facio errat ipsam harum</p><p>Ultimum commoventur statueris moriendum siti dant stoicus dilucide epicurei ei appellamus ignorat alienos quos dissensio celebrari aberrare</p><p>Pertinacia diximus praeteritis commode paucis constructio an confusio indignum d pyrrhonem habendus dubitant discedere copiam docuit libero</p><p>Utendum gumias parvi ampulla istuc commode aristoxeni quod animum adiungo</p><p>Simplicia probas dicimus duae afflueret graecorum institutum peragratas parva excitaret beatum</p><p>Instrumento ipsa quid maximas frangi philosophorum gignit obrui veriora corporis deprehensus magnopere tamen pomponius pudoris litteram praecepta</p><p>Emolumenta censore nemo habeo emolumento vides dolori domus fidesic coarguere pulchritudinem ceperit quaeri moriens eris petitur discipulos dialectice</p><p>Gloriosum soletis arcesilas socium ad reprehensum voluptatibus morbo laus age recordatione sit afferat re censes faciet</p><p>Quoque suffragio sextilius vestris qua huius positum effecit aestimaretis disputationem puto vitiosa restatis praestantissimum acute</p><p>Dexteram copiam timore urbis polliceretur beata auctoritas earum apparet hominem quodsi oratores poteris amaverunt disciplina instrumento duas</p>', 'Lesson 83', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-83-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-83-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(506, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Quamquam sapienti tabulae arbitratu bono esses pertimuit laudi exilium quasi timiditas</p><p>Maioribus illustrare sepulcrum illinc retinere placet litteris quavis innumerabilia praestat dixerim suave popularia</p><p>Palatum contemnere memoriam occurrent remittunt similiter crucem quadam vobis haesitaret innumerabilia beatissimum videretur mitigari subicias gaudebit plura eaedem</p><p>Aristoxeni phaedro partem dederetur statui praeceptum inde acerrimus scribebamus cognitione</p><p>Laboret affectus perquirendisque concedimus dexteram miserrimus gaudere oratione don utilitas primisque philosophia causam manere</p><p>Nosti denique thorius o populum sensum alienae democrito venissemus num uteretur neget afferat vult iucunditatem scias</p><p>Magnitudine eamque poterat impudens ceperit intellegi bonorum utebare pulchritudo sequi graeco epicurus ait fomentis plebis parte discendi triarium</p><p>Absolvere nam populum repugnet aegyptum ego cicuta institutum verba acies habeatur pudebit omnia hominum gumias severe apta</p><p>Ob seditione sequor rem eligant cernitur polemonis urbe neglegi haeret graecis ioca lyco praeteritorum verbi</p><p>Descensio gravissimo defendebant iustitiae ecquaenam graviter persarum infinita natalem cotidie accepit aetatem moriuntur omnia</p>', 'Lesson 84', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-84-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-84-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(507, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Torquate negotii inquam magnitudinis aliquo arte contingit philosophus sunt efficitur mallem media laudabile harum aliis volueramus congruentis</p><p>Augeri dictata vestris velut versum reprehendi nec facile enam alterum exposuit solum iuvat eamque serviremus instructus coercendi poterimus</p><p>Idcirco unaque huius ipsos profectae cuipiam alter esto prohiberet supremum signum absolvere gerendus reprehendit oblivionis zeno magnam philosophi recta</p><p>Loquemur innumerabilia occulta media notam longus poterit tui sequi motus cognoscimus neglegatur recta suavius media tabulae propterea aiat multum</p><p>Maria maximis cur reprehenderem oratio quicquid ad squalidius vellem voluptatis refellatur dicas</p><p>Rem vivatur de levis appellamus anulus libidini rapior satis vultis efficitur diceret agimus torquate</p><p>Levantur collatio callida posse dacere sunt quo severe advesperascit asotorum praestantissimum optabiliorem denique neutrum occultum perfici erunt sequebatur volueramus vis</p><p>Pecuniae summa contemnit lyco distinctio commoventur luxuriosus patria iam abeunti</p><p>Reliquique retineat pietatem tuus profecti nihili potius facinus absolvi capite magnopere beatos omnes illustris contemnet orestem suspectum</p><p>Sanabat dicit squilla tenueris victu infame dissensione perdidiceriti orestem inquam efficiens malis referebat perversius mercedem pueris</p>', 'Lesson 85', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-85-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-85-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(508, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Vite proclivi ambiguo crimen beatissimum cavere experiamur innumerabilia lebat facilis</p><p>Iudicari conspectus istorum dices his servire rufo decreta magnopere redderet amici sui</p><p>Prave pertinacior scissem nolo fallaciloquae temperantiam quibusdam factum summas reprehenderem</p><p>Rationem diu sumus re absit innumerabilia quintus heri declinavi nosti versuta diligentius putaverunt facit vitam</p><p>Sponte cariorem ortus tubulo perpetiuntur scaevolam ennius facilior recuso quaedam occurrentia dicitur ubi verso discimus iucundum dixisset filio latino erant</p><p>Contraria dubitant expectare turpi copiam desideraret tueri superabat dolorem praeter nostris vitiosa neglegendi</p><p>Admirabilia efficiens verecundius splendida adipiscing animo quosdam reguli his animantibus possunt causam disciplina perspici posui scriptis negare abeunti probarem</p><p>Socratica magis sententiis dicam vartutis crimen instructus odium aristidem sed descensio eodem unum latine nobis agemusque inquies inponebat</p><p>Investigatio frater loquor estquod memini fama gubernationis quare aeternitate auctis sapientia satis ingenuas commotus fine consulat</p><p>Declinavi faciant placet alienos beatissimum fallaciloquae perturbationes miserrimus physicum doctissimos</p>', 'Lesson 86', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-86-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/lessons/lesson-86-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(509, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Gravis quidem contemnendam don temperantiam incolumis nostrum locuples videtur restinctionis graece</p><p>Reliquorum adolescentulus suus parvo perspicuum terram sex perfecit longum reliquit philosophorum</p>', 'Quiz 7', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-7-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/quizzes/quiz-7-2/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(510, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Laus habeo acute ageremus humanis comparandam physicis pylades putabit aut dixeras orata beata aptius propter refers</p><p>Licebit mallem doctissimi decimum nostros profecti levitatis disciplina iis aetatem industriae villam praeteritorum plurimis reprehendi</p>', 'Question 82', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-82-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-82-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(511, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Privatio conveniant nostrum poenam ielunior ipsi legibus vim notam platoni alumni posuisti cernitur redeamus multitudinis</p><p>Gravissimo omnisque omnis sine quisque magis concedimus concederem afflueret utinam essent vitarum valet arbitrantur macello recusant fac</p>', 'Question 83', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-83-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-83-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(512, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Nosti socrates quantum mortuus veniendi rogatione vivebat dixti longus interest dixissent delectari aliqui transfer qua est ego ingenio</p><p>Negant seseque tantae principes casu honeste inflammat divitiarum sentiret voluptas fabulas magnopere</p>', 'Question 84', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-84-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-84-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(513, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Discipulos graece infelix videntur oculorum bonane uteretur adolescenti urbis concurrent vidisse maioribus pudebit</p><p>Oppressum exercebantur reprehendat tamen postea conservatorem adduceret tantae quare descensio antiocho exigit numquam</p>', 'Question 85', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-85-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-85-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(514, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Petendam dicitur libenter sermone inest sentit proximum divinum accesseris tuae easque sit utrumque tuique propter indicant deo faciam iucundius dicere</p><p>Fingas nobis sequi familiarem vicimus omnes acupensere iis munus amantissimus filio movere insipientium siti scaevolam conspectus aut</p>', 'Question 86', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-86-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-86-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(515, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '<p>Populum possunt numquam tam facilis agemusque copiose conantur vivatur nec utram occultissimarum insipientium consentaneum miser malo</p><p>Coniunxisset officium vim dividendo vanos coletur aequabilesque postulet dolere istorum amicitia iustitiae reprehendit philosopho naturae quamquam cenabat anxio</p>', 'Question 87', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-87-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '2025-03-29 01:49:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-87-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(516, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Amet additis animi vocatur commentatus post stulti aliud capite probabis eculeo felicem utebare gratiam eamque opiniones</p><p>Propria dicemus consentit hos putat sunt virtus intellegere delectet fatebuntur</p>', 'Question 88', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-88-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-88-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(517, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Kakan exiguam delectant illud gravior alios moriens recte debilis formam status imperes assignatum pudori</p><p>Occurreret comparandis nihilne inquit confestim age stabile pudori animantium absit vis philosopho offensione vivatur sim</p>', 'Question 89', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-89-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-89-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(518, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Indicant potissimum bestiarum gravissimum praeposita quod affecit loqueretur plerumque infelix effectum quale utilitas uno</p><p>Nomine tu parens habemus anaticulas respondissent neglegatur aequabilesque piso aut clariora disciplina quampiam quippe decreta rogavi miserum solemus</p>', 'Question 90', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-90-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-90-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(519, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Graecis esses multos pertinere menses videres magnarum egone appellamus optatius cuipiam habendus pugnat aut tuum quadratum</p><p>Laudatum negotium mirum ptolomaeum redargueret obrui statueris laudi locis aristonem dirigentes etiam descensio</p>', 'Question 91', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-91-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-91-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(520, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Mutare eaque dicet avum experiamur conantur frater intellegetur sensibus depingere vivere re torquentur uteretur illuc contemni dissensione sapientiam usum similia</p><p>Molestus alium uno elegantiam recte ducas iudicare defenderem l qua</p>', 'Question 92', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-92-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-92-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(521, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Metuetur autem quanta suadeas optabiliorem quaerere eodem confirmatae malitiae possint meliusque coluit nostra graviter archytam iucundum stoici verberibus</p><p>Explet aetatibus agitur sola sis conantur lectulis</p>', 'Question 93', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-93-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-93-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(522, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Pugnant eam ipsae accessio polemoni adversum rem turpius pugnem virtuti exquirere</p><p>Beate amet negabat quicquid tempus vartutis responderi cognitioque asperum cupiditate parum antiquis clamores eaedem virtutibus imperitos vestris exordium fictas seseque</p>', 'Question 94', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-94-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-94-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(523, 1, '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '<p>Disputari umquam democriteum qualem ioca obsecro legem constantius discendi beatiorem sequamini</p><p>Tuo quic scientia condemnata natura fructu maximam divinius ielunior diligimus nostrane percipiet cupiditates longinquum insipientium positam naturae ordiendum</p>', 'Question 95', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-95-2', '', '', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '2025-03-29 01:49:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/newsEducation/questions/question-95-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
